sentences.text:
J. Dorn was talking to an inmate who was standing in
Module B's vestibule.

layout_matches.text:
On 9/28/16 at about 0758 hours, Dep. J. Dorn was talking to an inmate who was standing in
Module B's vestibule. The inmate, Raymond Muniga (bk# 2955064) appeared agitated and
uncooperative. Dep. Dorn entered the vestibule through the hallway door with two additional
deputies, Dep. B. Tucker and Dep. C. Palomares-Velasco. Muniga assumed a fighting stance
and was holding one of his shoes in his hand. Dep. Dorn ordered Muniga two times to drop the
shoe and turn around to be cuffed. Muniga refused and said, "No." Dep. Dorn grabbed Muniga
by his shoulder. Muniga tried to turn away to break Dep. Dorn's grasp. Dep. Dorn, Tucker,
and Palomares-Velasco pulled Muniga to the ground to gain control. Muniga kicked Dep.
Palomares-Velasco several times, a violation of CPC 240/243(b). Five additional deputies
responded to help gain control of Muniga. Muniga was transported to OC Global Santa Ana to
be treated for his injuries.
